#: ../../typing.rst:2
msgid "Type Aliases"
msgstr "类型别名"

#: ../../typing.rst:4
msgid ""
"This module defines the type aliases used throughout CodeVideoRenderer for "
"type checking and autocompletion."
msgstr "本模块定义了 CodeVideoRenderer 中用于类型检查和自动补全的类型别名。"

#: ../../typing.rst:7
msgid "Quick reference"
msgstr "快速参考"

#: ../../typing.rst:9
msgid ""
":data:`~.PygmentsLanguage` — Valid language identifiers for syntax "
"highlighting (e.g. ``'python'``, ``'javascript'``)."
msgstr ""
":data:`~.PygmentsLanguage` — 语法高亮的有效语言标识符（例如 ``'python'``、``'javascript'``）。"

#: ../../typing.rst:10
msgid ""
":data:`~.PygmentsFormatterStyle` — Valid Pygments style names (e.g. "
"``'material'``, ``'github-dark'``, ``'monokai'``)."
msgstr ""
":data:`~.PygmentsFormatterStyle` — 有效的 Pygments 样式名称（例如 "
"``'material'``、``'github-dark'``、``'monokai'``）。"

#: ../../typing.rst:11
msgid ""
":data:`~.StrPath` — A ``str`` or ``os.PathLike`` representing a file system "
"path."
msgstr ":data:`~.StrPath` — 表示文件系统路径的 ``str`` 或 ``os.PathLike``。"

#: ../../typing.rst:15
msgid ""
"The lists above are not exhaustive. If you want to see every supported "
"language or style, run the sample code shown in the docstrings below."
msgstr "上面的列表并不详尽。如果您想查看所有支持的语言或样式，请运行下面 docstring 中显示的示例代码。"

#: of typing.Literal:1
msgid ""
"A string literal type representing programming languages supported by "
"Pygments for syntax highlighting. This type is used to ensure that only "
"valid language identifiers are accepted when specifying the language for "
"code rendering in the ``CodeVideoRenderer`` class. The list includes a wide "
"range of programming languages, markup languages, configuration file "
"formats, and other text-based formats that Pygments can recognize and "
"highlight appropriately."
msgstr ""
"一个字符串字面量类型，表示 Pygments 支持的用于语法高亮的编程语言。该类型用于确保在 ``CodeVideoRenderer`` "
"类中指定代码渲染语言时，只接受有效的语言标识符。列表包括多种编程语言、标记语言、配置文件格式，以及 Pygments "
"可以识别并正确高亮的其他基于文本的格式。"

#: of typing.Literal:6
msgid ""
"You can run the following code to get the complete list of supported "
"languages:"
msgstr "您可以运行以下代码获取支持的完整语言列表："

#: of typing.Literal:1
msgid ""
"A string literal type representing formatter styles supported by Pygments "
"for syntax highlighting. This type is used to ensure that only valid "
"formatter styles are accepted when specifying the formatter style for code "
"rendering in the ``CodeVideoRenderer`` class. The list includes a variety of"
" styles that can be applied to the syntax highlighting, ranging from light "
"and dark themes to styles designed for accessibility and specific color "
"schemes."
msgstr ""
"一个字符串字面量类型，表示 Pygments 支持的用于语法高亮的格式化器样式。该类型用于确保在 ``CodeVideoRenderer`` "
"类中指定代码渲染的格式化器样式时，只接受有效的样式。列表包括多种可应用于语法高亮的样式，涵盖浅色和深色主题，以及专为无障碍和特定配色方案设计的样式。"

#: of typing.Literal:6
msgid ""
"You can run the following code to get the complete list of supported "
"formatter styles:"
msgstr "您可以运行以下代码获取支持的完整格式化器样式列表："

#: of typing.Union:1
msgid ""
"A string or ``os.PathLike`` representing a path to a directory or file."
msgstr "表示目录或文件路径的字符串或 ``os.PathLike``。"

#~ msgid "Typings"
#~ msgstr "类型定义"
